n = int(input())
d = [int(x) for x in input().split()]

x = d[0]
y = d[0]
for i in range(1, n):
    if d[i] % x == 0:
        y *= d[i]
    else:
        x *= d[i]

print(x, y)

n = int(input())
d = [int(x) for x in input().split()]

x = d[0]  # первый элемент массива
y = d[0]  # первый элемент массива

for i in range(1, n):
    if d[i] % x == 0:  # если остаток от деления элемента массива на x равен нулю

        x *= d[i]

print(x, y)

n = int(input())
divisors = [int(i) for i in input().split()]

divisors.sort()

x = 1
y = 1
for i in range(n):
    if i % 2 == 0:
        x *= divisors[i]
    else:
        y *= divisors[i]

print(x, y)

n = int(input())
d = [int(x) for x in input().split()]

x = 1
y = 1

for i in range(1, n):
    if d[i] % x != 0:
        x *= d[i]
    elif d[i] % y != 0:
        y *= d[i]

print(x, y)
